Wyckoff Ave. (trolley thereon), north side, west of Madison Street to Myrtle Ave. and Palmetto Street (Elevated structure thereon.) This is a set of three views. John Welz established his brewery in 1859 on Scholes Street at Graham Avenue. He moved his business to its present location in 1861. In 1883, John Welz Jr. and C.D. Zerweck took over the plant.

1922.
View 2: October 1928.
View 3: March 1924.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
